<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-03-21 13:20:06.209045</lastBuildDate><item><title>nothing else to say</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KCLrOhi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GaBChqo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love them with all my heart. Sobbing as I write this but I truly don’t know what else to do. 

I found out last week that my cancer is no longer in remission and unless I can undergo treatment snd surgery again, I only have a few months. I’ve been out of work and lost my insurance so it’s not looking good for me.

I want to be responsible and take care of my sweet girls, but I have no family who will take them and it’s getting hard for me to take care of them. I’ve posted about them but no one wants them due to their ages (15 & 18).

If you’re in the Central Florida area and would like two quiet sweet persians or if you know of a place taking senior cats, please let me know, you can message me on Imgur. 

I’m extremely afraid of bringing them to a shelter and I’m hoping to find a great home for them in the next few weeks.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lpnyeSj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KvQXwG6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IGL4XBy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1qW8sfy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>thank you for the info! their names are penny and puka. they are calico persians, both female. sleep a lot and love their rainbow wand toy, and squirrel watching. very laidback, sweet cats, and ok with most dogs. they grew up with a corgi and dachshund.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KCLrOhi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DanHeavenly]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I never thought I would make it this far…</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/V4lMACm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hq2mnY4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It wasn’t an easy ride. I had to fund my own degree and accomodation by creating a tutoring business. I couch hopped and borrowed money from friends to get here. But I’m here, and past me would be so very very proud and impressed. 

We made it.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/V4lMACm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JoleneJoleneJoleneJoleeene]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Lol lol :)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ncJeGay</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eTSSLhq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pet_foolery https://www.instagram.com/pet_foolery/?hl=en</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/A4SJKyO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vjdTY1Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LxYQodG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XXRChGA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BGDScMS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/70v2yLU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rOEdMQv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ncJeGay</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheRainbowegoSweet007]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Community</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/cUmcs1v</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ThZVgzz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/cUmcs1v</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DaiMudda]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>And punished the most if said work isn’t done.  Never fired though</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EHNLbac</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DfZrBrm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; hei